                        </p>

                    </li>

                    <li>
                        <b>3. ChangePassword.cshtml</b> ('Find View inside Views Folder  &raquo; User Folder &raquo; ChangePassword.cshtml')
                        <p>
                            A View is also a one Class. so in this Page we are using Html.BeginForm to perform Edit operation.
                        </p>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <hr>
                <a style="float:left" href="/Home/Designing">Design Used</a> <a style="float:right" href="/Home/Information">Application Info</a>
